Class ForceFieldGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • item.Item
      • item.ForceFieldGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Activatable, VisitableItem, java.util.Observer, MovableEffect

    public class ForceFieldGenerator
extends Item
implements Activatable, java.util.Observer
    The ForceFieldGenerator generates a line segment between another force field generator if it is within an appropriate distance The Generator holds a reference to the line segment. This line segment switches on and off.
    Author:
    vincentreniers
